   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>VrS20.13 Var. a (mss. 2000, 2065):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>yaϑā ahū vairiiō</em> čahār az pāy pad buland guftan čīyōn pad yašt tā bagām sar</ab>  
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "They should recite four <em>yaϑā ahū vairiiō</em>, standing and in loud voice like in the <em>yašt</em> until the end of the <em>bagām</em>."</ab>
         
         <ab>VrS20.13 Var. b (mss. 2007, 2030, 2106, 2109, 4050, 5020):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>yaϑā ahū vairiiō</em> čahār pad buland wāng guftan ud frāgām abrāstan</ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "They should recite four <em>yaϑā ahū vairiiō</em> in loud voice und to raise the <em>frāgām</em>."</ab>  
      </Nerangs>
